 Ridley,"],[7982,8045,"I see what you're"],[8045,8116,"trying to do and I'm gonna"],[8116,8224,"have to ask you to stop."]],"60":[[0,129,"I don't know what you're talking about."],[162,308,"Mateo and I are old friends."],[392,571,"That may be true, but he's"],[654,767,"my husband now."],[909,955,"And you're gonna"],[955,1042,"learn to respect that."],[1088,1247,"Let me go, are you crazy?"],[1297,1468,"What's crazy is you thinking"],[1468,1580,"that you can walk around the"],[1580,1668,"playground trying to steal"],[1668,1751,"other people's toys"],[1751,1889,"without consequences."],[1964,2102,"It's not gonna make you many friends,"],[2102,2206,"is it?"],[2398,2540,"Thank you for having us."],[2635,2702,"I think we're gonna walk"],[2702,2756,"around a little."],[2852,2923,"As you said,"],[3073,3115,"I've never been to"],[3115,3211,"a party like this."],[3261,3415,"Better make the most of it."],[3787,3958,"You sneaky bitch,"],[3958,4062,"Chloe Pascal."],[4145,4283,"I'm telling the whole world who"],[4283,4425,"Mateo really is."],[6060,6135,"Good evening."],[6202,6331,"Thank you all for attending"],[6331,6489,"the Ridley Charity Gala."],[6560,6690,"As a Ridley heiress,"],[6710,6785,"I have an important"],[6785,6902,"announcement to make."],[7190,7248,"Wait,"],[7248,7357,"that's my family heirloom."],[7394,7528,"This ring belongs to the"],[7528,7624,"Nela Corporation."],[7678,7770,"That's right,"],[7795,7887,"I'm engaged to"],[7887,8041,"the CEO of Nela Corp."],[8153,8241,"In fact,"],[8279,8400,"he's here in this room."],[8533,8637,"Ladies and gentlemen,"],[8666,8904,"Mateo Lane, the CEO in hiding."]],"61":[[179,271,"What is she talking about?"],[346,462,"Listen to me, okay?"],[513,613,"Don't listen to her."],[617,788,"You own Nela Corp?"],[1017,1055,"Yes."],[1117,1267,"Nela Lane."],[1359,1393,"Wait."],[1693,1776,"Be honest."],[1910,1972,"Where did you get"],[1972,2052,"all of this stuff?"],[2168,2293,"The guards, the money,"],[2498,2610,"who are you really?"],[2740,2894,"Mr. Miles borrowed"],[2923,3048,"all this stuff from the CEO."],[3303,3340,"Hey,"],[3357,3503,"Why would you lie to me?"],[3720,3799,"Did you think that I was"],[3799,3916,"gonna come after your money?"],[3920,4016,"No, no,"],[4058,4195,"-no 10 years."],[4229,4391,"I've known you for 10 years."],[4391,4525,"Like you were my best friend."],[4546,4700,"I am, I am."],[4704,4813,"I thought you were the one"],[4813,4917,"person in this world that I"],[4917,5013,"could actually trust."],[5042,5100,"You can."],[5150,5180,"Chloe."],[5405,5476,"No, it was real."],[5693,5809,"I'm begging you, okay?"],[5822,5868,"Just..."],[5972,6056,"Please,"],[6089,6156,"please,"],[6156,6260,"don't listen to her, okay?"],[6260,6373,"Let me explain."],[6410,6435,"I can-"],[6435,6577,"Then explain, Mateo."],[6669,6844,"Explain why you lied to me."],[6844,7019,"Explain why you married me."],[7048,7144,"But there's another woman"],[7144,7278,"wearing your family's"],[7278,7361,"heirloom wedding ring."],[7361,7436,"I don't know how she"],[7436,7557,"got the ring, okay?"],[7620,7766,"Listen, I promise you on my"],[7766,7874,"whole life, I have no idea"],[7874,7945,"how she got that."],[7945,8087,"I did not give that to her."],[8087,8158,"I don't know."],[8245,8350,"I gave it to her."],[8558,8604,"Mom?"]],"62":[[437,542,"I'm gonna say this once,"],[571,658,"and one time only."],[721,800,"So you listen,"],[846,913,"legally,"],[988,1096,"Chloe is my wife."],[1096,1167,"Do you understand?"],[1238,1330,"So that ring does"],[1330,1422,"not belong to her."],[1514,1618,"It belongs to Chloe."],[1693,1793,"That ring"],[1805,1993,"is worth 10 million dollars, Mateo."],[2022,2077,"It's our most"],[2077,2214,"valuable family heirloom."],[2214,2356,"There is no way"],[2385,2610,"I am letting it go to this"],[2686,2802,"lowly nobody."],[3228,3319,"I thought she was some"],[3319,3432,"heiress herself."],[3536,3653,"All dolled up like that."],[3699,3795,"Turns out she's just a"],[3795,3924,"wanna be gold digger."],[3987,4095,"That's embarrassing."],[4162,4225,"Well,"],[4300,4383,"I guess spreading her"],[4383,4550,"legs only got her this far."],[4758,4925,"I didn't know who Mateo was."],[4946,5067,"I wasn't with him"],[5067,5201,"for the money, and"],[5338,5447,"I've never asked"],[5447,5555,"anything of him."],[5751,5851,"Even if that was true,"],[5918,5993,"I still don't"],[5993,6110,"approve of this marriage."],[6206,6302,"Just look at Jane,"],[6327,6418,"she's a Ridley,"],[6473,6602,"the richest family in this city."],[6702,6852,"She can help our business"],[6852,6969,"reach a new height."],[7107,7178,"But you,"],[7344,7415,"you're nothing,"],[7511,7636,"and you have"],[7670,7870,"nothing to offer."],[8087,8195,"I had attorneys draft this"],[8195,8291,"divorce paper."],[8320,8425,"Sign it"],[8450,8504,"now!"],[8737,8871,"Here’s 1 billion dollars."],[8904,9096,"Divorce Mateo and it’s yours!"],[9096,9188,"Okay, that's enough!"],[9288,9330,"Listen,"],[9446,9559,"I will never"],[9605,9730,"take your money,"],[9730,9864,"and I will never be part of"],[9864,10047,"your world walking all over"],[10047,10143,"people just because you're"],[10143,10310,"rich and powerful."],[10514,10560,"So,"],[10777,10852,"I'll sign."],[10852,10919,"Chloe."]],"63":[[16,145,"You don't have to do this."],[171,225,"Look,"],[275,467,"it really hurts knowing"],[467,625,"that you've been lying to me"],[625,779,"this whole time."],[921,967,"But,"],[1063,1313,"I think I understand why you did it."],[1355,1509,"You and I come from very"],[1509,1651,"different worlds and"],[1680,1860,"being best friends and"],[1860,1981,"pretending that was..."],[2056,2268,"That was the only way for us"],[2268,2377,"to actually be in each"],[2377,2456,"other's lives."],[2660,2777,"You ready to burn the bridge?"],[2886,2994,"Because once we do,"],[3053,3186,"there's no turning back."],[3224,3299,"Yes,"],[3349,3457,"I'm ready Mateo."],[3641,3762,"I'm ready to be more than"],[3762,3899,"just best friends with you."],[4066,4304,"I fell for you and that's"],[4304,4454,"why I'm losing you."],[4696,4754,"Wait!"]],"64":[[196,254,"Daddy,"],[291,396,"I... I thought you were at"],[396,508,"a conference in Europe."],[713,763,"I'm the one who"],[763,842,"invited Derek here."],[884,992,"And I'm glad you did, Mateo."],[1034,1101,"Otherwise, I wouldn't have"],[1101,1230,"known that Jane was using our"],[1230,1388,"family gala as a chance to"],[1388,1493,"bully your wife."],[1530,1676,"Derek, what are you talking about?"],[1676,1730,"No one is"],[1730,1885,"bullying anyone here."],[1960,2056,"I'm just trying to talk some"],[2056,2147,"sense into her."],[2218,2318,"Of course, she can't compete"],[2318,2394,"with your daughter."],[2494,2581,"That's just the truth."],[2627,2673,"That's right."],[2727,2811,"She's about to sign the"],[2811,2902,"divorce papers"],[2927,3011,"and leave with a check."],[3132,3203,"She's nothing but a"],[3203,3303,"greedy gold digger,"],[3303,3361,"Daddy."],[3399,3553,"Didn't you just bribe her"],[3553,3712,"with the check that she"],[3712,3774,"ripped in half,"],[3774,3895,"or am I mistaken?"],[4137,4200,"You should be ashamed of"],[4200,4275,"yourself, Jane."],[4350,4525,"What you've done is in no way"],[4525,4587,"how a true"],[4587,4667,"Ridley would behave."],[4692,4758,"But daddy,"],[4796,4842,"I should be"],[4842,4938,"marrying Mateo."],[4938,5092,"I'm the Ridley heiress."],[5125,5284,"Indeed, Derek, only your"],[5284,5392,"daughter is worthy"],[5392,5530,"enough of my son."],[5563,5630,"Wait a minute."],[5751,5880,"So the only reason that the"],[5880,5951,"two of you want me to marry"],[5951,6039,"her is because you think that"],[6039,6164,"she's the Ridley heiress?"],[6227,6277,"Yes."],[6548,6731,"I have a DNA test result right here"],[6777,6881,"that proves that you"],[6977,7086,"are not in the family."],[7102,7186,"You are not the"],[7186,7265,"Ridley heiress."],[7315,7399,"Chloe"],[7515,7615,"is the Ridley heiress."],[7649,7741,"Or should I say,"],[7903,8058,"