 gonna kill you bitch!"],[1297,1401,"Take her to the police!"],[1755,1830,"Oh my God."],[1889,1951,"You're hurt."],[1956,2027,"That's fine."],[2289,2318,"Hey,"],[2469,2548,"Chloe, why are you bleeding?"],[2652,2677,"Hey."],[2677,2727,"Mateo."],[2786,2831,"Help!"],[2869,2957,"I‘m pregnant!"],[3011,3036,"What?"],[3107,3140,"Chloe."],[3215,3261,"Tom!"],[3299,3386,"Call 911, now."],[3482,3511,"Chloe."],[3578,3611,"Chloe."],[3632,3762,"Hey, hey, hey, stay with me."],[3774,3845,"Stay with me."],[3845,3870,"Hey."],[3916,3953,"Hey."],[4333,4441,"Oh, I'm so glad you're awake."],[4692,4808,"I thought that I lost you."],[4929,4971,"What?"],[4988,5042,"The baby."]],"69":[[187,308,"The baby is healthy"],[308,421,"and safe and sound."],[517,583,"Just like you."],[734,842,"You saved me."],[1055,1188,"You saved our baby."],[1580,1639,"I can't believe"],[1639,1743,"we're gonna have a baby."],[1926,2068,"Our baby."],[2206,2306,"Your baby?"]],"70":[[37,150,"Your baby?"],[362,437,"Hey, Mom."],[517,621,"Chloe just woke up, so"],[621,725,"whatever you're here for..."],[754,863,"Mateo, I just"],[863,950,"want to talk to her."],[996,1067,"It's okay, Mateo."],[1259,1422,"Mrs. Lane, just hear me out."],[1447,1730,"You married my son behind my back,"],[1789,1906,"then you got him hurt."],[1993,2097,"And now you're telling me"],[2097,2285,"that you're carrying his child?"],[2348,2414,"I don't even"],[2414,2498,"know what to say."],[2698,2806,"Except thank you."],[3057,3253,"Yes, maybe I was shocked to"],[3253,3353,"find out about you."],[3424,3478,"And..."],[3524,3578,"Yes,"],[3632,3887,"maybe I cared too much about him"],[3916,4058,"marrying the right girl from"],[4058,4166,"the right family."],[4325,4437,"But seeing everything you've"],[4437,4542,"gone through together,"],[4579,4742,"I can see that you are the"],[4742,4871,"right girl for him."],[5259,5380,"And she is, turns out,"],[5380,5497,"from the right family."],[5551,5626,"Mr. Ridley."],[5638,5764,"I know it will take some time"],[5784,5885,"to get to this, Chloe."],[5885,6010,"But, call me Dad."],[6068,6143,"What?"],[6185,6289,"You're my real daughter."],[6423,6489,"And the rightful"],[6489,6602,"Ridley heiress."],[6744,6981,"All of my trophies and treasures"],[6981,7140,"will be yours one day."],[7207,7399,"What I did was unacceptable,"],[7444,7624,"and I'd like to apologize."],[7820,7953,"I brought a peace offering,"],[7987,8179,"a belated wedding gift for you."],[8237,8370,"It's the matching necklace to"],[8370,8479,"the diamond ring."],[8575,8717,"The most precious heirloom of"],[8717,8817,"the Lane family."]],"71":[[104,291,"It's the matching necklace to"],[291,396,"the diamond ring."],[471,633,"The most precious heirloom of"],[633,734,"the Lane family."],[813,959,"I trusted that ring to the"],[959,1067,"wrong woman, Chloe."],[1134,1255,"This time I want to"],[1255,1338,"make things right."],[1418,1539,"Thank you, Mrs. Lane."],[2181,2268,"There you have it."],[2356,2435,"You are"],[2456,2560,"officially a part of"],[2560,2698,"the Lane family now."],[2731,2827,"And our baby."],[3261,3353,"I'm sorry I didn't"],[3353,3470,"tell you earlier."],[3470,3578,"I was planning on telling you"],[3578,3682,"after the callup."],[3682,3803,"No, no, no, no."],[3824,3924,"Hey, it's my fault."],[3999,4049,"I should have told"],[4049,4179,"you who I really was."],[4266,4312,"No."],[4479,4546,"Mateo,"],[4692,4900,"you stood by me for 10 years."],[4900,4950,"You..."],[5017,5096,"protected me"],[5096,5201,"from my family."],[5251,5347,"You gave me a house"],[5347,5476,"when I needed it most."],[5563,5768,"No one knows me or loves me"],[5768,5905,"the way you do."]],"72":[[100,191,"See that?"],[291,354,"Mommy and daddy"],[354,467,"are getting married."],[625,675,"Again."],[1067,1146,"They say,"],[1267,1338,"that if you get to"],[1338,1447,"marry your best friend,"],[1459,1609,"you're the lucky one."],[1847,2056,"For 11 years, Mateo Lane,"],[2072,2231,"you were my best friend."],[2364,2548,"Until one night,"],[2656,2898,"you became more than that."],[3103,3307,"And I wasn't sure at first."],[3349,3465,"I didn't want to lose you."],[3578,3636,"And I was afraid"],[3636,3732,"to take that leap."],[3807,3966,"But time after time,"],[4029,4124,"you showed me."],[4266,4391,"It's okay to take those"],[4391,4567,"chances when you're with the"],[4567,4650,"one that you love."],[4842,4934,"And that's you."],[5105,5213,"It's always been you."],[5367,5488,"I love you, Mateo."],[5555,5663,"I've loved you since the day"],[5663,5755,"that I met you."],[5914,5972,"And then"],[6060,6160,"when I was scared to"],[6160,6281,"tell you everything about me,"],[6281,6377,"show you every"],[6435,6519,"piece of me,"],[6660,6781,"reveal my secrets,"],[6781,6923,"things that no one else knows,"],[7057,7257,"you made that so safe."],[7257,7328,"And then"],[7424,7524,"I fell in love with"],[7524,7632,"you so much more in ways"],[7632,7803,"I didn't even know was possible."],[8095,8245,"You truly are my best friend."],[8308,8395,"And I love you."],[8508,8533,"So,"],[8625,8679,"Chloe,"],[8779,8833,"what do you say to"],[8833,8992,"being best friends forever?"],[9175,9225,"Yes."],[9376,9501,"Forever and ever."]]}